+# CartView Review — 2026-04-15
+
+Canonical discussion artifact:
+- `pipeline/chain-state/cartview-260415-213231-403a-codex-position.md`
+
+## Verdict
+
+Main conclusions from the Codex discussion pass:
+
+- CV-BUG-07 does not look live in current HEAD because `pages/PublicMenu/x.jsx:1159-1167` already rounds inside `formatPrice`; local rounding in `CartView` would be optional hardening.
+- CV-BUG-08 should follow the newer CV-70 decision dated 2026-04-14: empty cart with existing orders uses primary `Вернуться в меню`, not outline `Заказать ещё`.
+- CV-BUG-09 is still real: `CartView` maps table-tab status from the stage label, not `internal_code`, so `Готово` can leak to guests.
+- CV-BUG-10 should remove both `Счёт стола` cards and use a `Стол`-tab header label `Заказано на стол`, sourced from submitted `sessionOrders` only, not `tableTotal` because `tableTotal` includes cart money.
+- CV-BUG-11 should remove the `Оценить блюда гостей` button from the `Стол` tab UI; deeper hook cleanup can wait.
+- CV-BUG-12 should replace the raw-ID fallback with a human ordinal fallback `Гость N`; the real data-sync cause belongs in a later batch.
+- CV-BUG-13 should use a small local plural helper plus 3 i18n keys.
+- CV-BUG-06 should filter cancelled orders by `getOrderStatus(o).internal_code`, with raw `o.status` only as legacy fallback.
+
+## Prompt Clarity
+
+- Overall clarity: 3/5
+- Main ambiguities:
+  - Q1 conflicts with the current rounded formatter in `pages/PublicMenu/x.jsx`.
+  - Q2 conflicts with the stale State B row in the UX spec versus the newer CV-70 decision log dated 2026-04-14.
+  - Q4 mixes multiple candidate totals, while the later frozen spec clarifies that `Заказано на стол` means submitted orders of all guests.
+  - External sibling `pipeline` paths were required for writes, but those paths are outside the writable sandbox roots in this session.
